175
00:10:43,618 --> 00:10:45,061
Mets ton pantalon de bus.

176
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:54,477
{\pub}{\pos(192,200)}J'ai rêvé qu'on devenait super riches
grâce à l'application

177
00:10:54,644 --> 00:10:57,156
